Class Organism

  • java.lang.Object
    • Organisms.Organism
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bluejay, Caterpillar, Deer, Fox, Grass, Grasshopper, Hawk, Mouse, Rabbit, Squirrel, TreeOrShrubs, Wolf
    public class Organism
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    lane203m class for all organisms. Parent class. All organisms extend from this. Contains name, nickname, what they eat, if they can move or are fed, their x/y coords Contains the eat, move, get functions and constructors for the organisms
